{"id":"d8419ba5-5368-435e-9a27-a2bdf911883a","name":"Fleur","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Your new boss is very... unique.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">﹒୨𝑒 ﾟ ˖</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>WLW</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/04bab73f-e7d2-4f23-bbe7-a882665a3a23_556e2944-ab8f-4db0-933e-c656091dc53c.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You recently started working at Fleur's bakery, and everything was going fine, except that she is, frankly, weird. Most of the time she's silent and deadpan, paying you no mind.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Most </em>of the time... except those odd moments when she gets too close, too touchy, with no explanation why.</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/04bab73f-e7d2-4f23-bbe7-a882665a3a23_556e2944-ab8f-4db0-933e-c656091dc53c.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/04bab73f-e7d2-4f23-bbe7-a882665a3a23_71545db6-8891-41d2-a2d8-9dafde64899f.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 137, 137)\">9999mme on twt</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/04bab73f-e7d2-4f23-bbe7-a882665a3a23_ce39bee7-2881-4f85-b817-55efa700ca2a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"04bab73f-e7d2-4f23-bbe7-a882665a3a23_a5af440b-507b-471e-a4bf-98aef5ae61b8.webp","creator":"yivy","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","⛓️ Domina